Subject: Love Hacked? 36 Questions That May Change Your Life
Description: Can there be a formula to the way our feelings grow for each other? Some say a series of 36 questions can create emotional intimacy in a very short period of time, even among strangers. Come and join our experiment to see such claims hold true!  Couples encouraged if space allows.  This panel is for ages 18+ only. Minors are not allowed (with or without a parent). Participation will depend on demographically matching partner availability. Due to the nature of the activity, attendance will be limited. Please sign up in advance at Ops.  Speakers include:Edward Fleece - Track: After Dark  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes
